Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tomb Stones are playing\Nat the Portside Concert Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really?\N-Tickets go on sale today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's that?\N-You've never heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Tomb Stones? They're hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dense about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,SOLD OUT\NALL TICKETS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They sold out before noon.\NWe didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you girls!\NDid you come to buy tickets too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad. They're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have waited\Nin line last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a school day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's only one day!\N-What a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,DANGER, DO NOT TOUCH!\NSUPER ELECTRIC TRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, dear. Would you\Nlike some Russian tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? All right.\NI'll show you a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll put a smile on any sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now feeling happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NSo happy you want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you feel like laughing.\NYou're so happy, you want to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to hug your dad\Nfor making you so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's working.\NNow for the final touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickets to the Tomb Stones concert!\NHow did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A client gave them to me, but I'm\Njust not into loud music like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're not good seats, though.\N-That doesn't matter! Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She changes so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two tickets. Who should I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira's not interested\Nin this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoko and Ryoko would be thrilled,\Nbut they're bound to fight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he would be happy to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...but wouldn't it be\Nsort of like a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Catch you later.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Too bad about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so upset, I couldn't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar, we're late because\Nyou overslept today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm missing my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Emi! Let me see your homework!\N-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Meimi, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it?\N-Well....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have these tickets--\N-Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Tomb Stones fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tickets to the concert!\N-And front row seats too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you get these?\N-From my uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way!\N-Hey, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-How about it?\N-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did you want?\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-You started to say something.\N-Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina will get mad if\Nshe catches you talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, neither do l!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for entering unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite all right.\NDo you have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I only make metal monuments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Daisuke Noguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were given many awards\Nat one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I had it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been in a slump\Nfor some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was recognized as a real sculptor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...only after I made\Nthe Steel Weathercock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, I borrowed a space\Nin a workshop and did odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was\Nto create a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as I unveiled\Nthe weathercock...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...my life changed.\NAll my past hardships like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Steel Weathercock\Nwas my lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wouldn't sell it,\Nno matter how much anyone offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was stolen a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't been able\Nto finish a piece since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,These past six months\Nhave been particularly bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then recently I learned\Nthat my sculpture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...is being displayed atop\Nthe Misato building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You must contact the building's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did that! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The weathercock is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I purchased that piece\Nfrom a legitimate art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's not possible!\N-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the contract.\NWell? Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, these documents aren't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have complaints,\Ngo to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I warn you, I do have\Nthe documents to prove...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...I bought the sculpture,\Nso there's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless, of course,\Nyou offer to buy it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have promised to sell it to\Na businessman in Hong Kong next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So decide quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!\NI'm lost without my sculpture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating since\NI can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When will he sell it\Nto that businessman in Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be removed three days\Nfrom now. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he gets the sculpture back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure he will be able\Nto create more pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Meimi? Meimi!\N-Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Since there's\Nno time, maybe we should reconsider--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! If we forsake a person in trouble,\Nwe'll damage St. Tail's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it back for him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow.\NThe same night as the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.\NIt won't be fun going alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he go to the concert or--?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pull a job\Nwithout giving him a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!\NWhat time should we meet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you talking about?\N-The concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come with me,\Nor give me back your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will steal the Steel Weathercock\Ntoday from the Misato building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! The concert's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about St. Tail!\NWe're going to the concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bothersome situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do your utmost\Nto capture her at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completing the sale\Ntomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come\Nto own that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it, of course.\NFrom an art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail never steals anything\Nfrom its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a petty thief,\Nwith no reason for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you taking her side\Non this issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, the mayor and I\Nare close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can easily have you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you mind\Nletting me see that sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. If St. Tail is\Narrested, they'll know we stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if she can't talk\Nwhen she's captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For security, a high voltage current\Nruns through the sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One touch and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even St. Tail can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insane! She'll be--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All it means is a foolish\Nthief was electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter. After all,\Nshe is just a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-I won't allow that!\N-It's time for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Let me go!\NHey, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they don't\Nneed our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny, no one's around. Maybe\Nhe went to the concert after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't do anything, you got that?\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wired with electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it! But for now....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You won't get away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let her escape! After her!\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She went into quadrant 24C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's there?\N-Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one downstairs,\Nso I just came on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'll be locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe my son came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, earlier, but he gave up and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. President--!\N-It's okay. He's about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've trapped St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the cooler on.\NMake sure it's on full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-But Asuka Jr.'s in there too.\N-So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for helping me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-You've got a lot of guts.\N-So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this really headstrong girl\Nin my class too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut we always end up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to, it just happens.\NWe had a fight today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't know why, but she was mad.\N-You're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could have been\Nto blame too. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to do something\Nor we'll freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, son, you in there?\N-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can break through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-I knew you were up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Come back here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the sculpture! Give\Nmy best to your headstrong friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:18:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Things look bad.\NNow that Asuka Jr.'s out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If his father investigates,\Nwe're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hobby is\Ncollecting stolen artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not being cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, look at all this!\NThese are all listed as stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have quite a collection.\NMore than rumored!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, why are you two blushing?\N-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! Where were you\Nyesterday? I waited all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you two together last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NI wouldn't be caught dead--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts, Meimi!
